channel.title: Rune-World anti leech fixed
channel.description:
I'm tired of seeing topics about this in the server help section so here ;).
The so called 'anti - leech' could hardly be considered an anti leech as it was a missing bracket under a break statement on case 13405: and a packaging problem, I have no clue where he got the missing transient variable part from, but there was nothing missing.
The server it's self has all of the original content nothing was touched, the only thing that was modified was the anti leech.
If you get a [b]path not specified[/b] error, simply right click the run batch file and change this jdk1.6.0_## to whatever version of java you have. Also, if you're running a 64-bit pc you will need to make a modification to this /Program Files/ You just need to add a (x86) at the end. Enjoy
This doesn't have the client, just the server. http://up.ht/OYxyKO http://uppit.com/vu1tbmd61cjr/Rune-World_Fixed.rar
EDIT: Okay, since I've already got a million pms about the client I uploaded it. http://up.ht/OYOwc1 http://uppit.com/qs11qndvwevt/Rune-World_Client.rar
To change the IP simply go into client class (client.java) and search for the string server = "127.0.0.1".
[quote="hottys2good4, post:1, topic:446982"][u][b]Some Features:[/b][/u]
[b]Skills:[/b] Perfect combat All 24 skills are fully trainable, even farming, construction, etc Skilling arena to help you level up Ancient and lunar magic Ancient curses, so you can use that amazing turmoil 100% working range and magic Great leveling up Double XP events Real pking and drops, just like Runescape!
[b]Minigames:[/b] Zombies (NEW) Pyramid Plunder Domination Tower Barrows Pest Control Duel Arena Castle Wars Tzhaar Fight Caves Tzhaar Fight Pits Barbarian Assault Warrior's Guild
[b]Monsters:[/b] Frost Dragons Complete GWD, with all 4 gods Giant Mole, with real burrowing Strykywerms Tormented Demons Kalphite Queen KBD Daggonoth Kings Chaos Elemental Everlasting Nomad Corporal Beast Dungeoneering Monsters Complete Brimhaven Dungeon Complete Taverly Dungeon Complete Slayer Tower Complete Varrock Sewers 100+ Other Spawned NPC's to be trained on.
Items: ALL Chaotic Weapons Extreme Potions Royal Torva Dicing and Gambling Few Customs Dragon Claws Koraski Ceremonial Colored Whips Many, many new Runescape items. [b] Much more features, cba to list them all...[/b]
[u][b]~Media~[/b][/u] [b]Zombies Video:[/b] http://youtu.be/ymo_PWrjwhg [img]http://i.imgur.com/sQItT.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/U1wc1.png[/img] Cbf to add more media...[/quote]
